{"tid":2207694,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登警告 若英國退歐危及北愛協議 美國將不會與英達成貿易協議","createTime":"2020-09-18T10:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T12:47:24.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"def3453a2bc33cccd1ddf236a3c1ec025492722c","tid":2207694,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:34:59.000Z","msg":"路透倫敦9月17日 - 美國民主黨總統候選人拜登(Joe Biden)警告英國，脫離歐盟需遵守北愛爾蘭1998年和平協議，否則美國將不會與英國達成單獨的貿易協定。<br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜提出一項新法案，將違反英國退歐協議中涉及北愛爾蘭邊境的條款。<br />\n<br />\n「我們不容給北愛爾蘭帶來和平的貝爾法斯特協議(Good Friday Agreement )變成英國退歐下的犧牲品。」拜登週三在推特上稱。<br />\n<br />\n「美國和英國間的任何貿易協議，都必須取決於尊重該協議，並防止恢復硬邊界。就是這樣。」<br />\n<br />\n法國興業銀行分析師週四稱，他們目前認為英國和歐盟年底前無法敲定貿易協議的機率達80%。<br />\n<br />\n拜登轉發了美國眾議院外交事務委員會主席Eliot Engel給約翰遜的推文，該推文勸告約翰遜遵守貝爾法斯特協議。(完)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.reuters.com/article/biden-brexit-north-ireland-0918-idCNKBS26909M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fbiden-brexit-north-ireland-0918-idCNKBS26909M&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdQ1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=07ae5672\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fbiden-brexit-north-ireland-0918-idCNKBS26909M&h=762cc8fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.reuters.com/article/biden-brexit-north-ireland-0918-idCNKBS26909M</a>"},{"pid":"b87b06601a4784c4e09290ac32b10073bfad7916","tid":2207694,"uid":370061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:38:05.000Z","msg":"你選到啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17f998914abb69c2cab91ad48483b9a8ee1e93c","tid":2207694,"uid":80724,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:50:45.000Z","msg":"咁更加唔可以比你選到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9890118fba576202e50cec7ff516a779553cd33d","tid":2207694,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T12:45:06.000Z","msg":"China Joe <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83be26d5554acaa1a789d66b34f8888554971d38","tid":2207694,"uid":182653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T12:47:24.000Z","msg":"你邊位呀<br />\n雖然連登好支持你姐"}]}